---
const afterImageSrc = `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/despues.png`;
---
<section class="hero reveal">
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Tus propiedades, irresistibles. <br/>En 48 horas.</h1>
        <p>Fotografía profesional y decoración virtual diseñada para atraer más consultas y acelerar el proceso de venta.</p>
        
        <div class="hero-actions">
            <button class="btn-wizard" id="heroWizardBtn" type="button">Probar el sistema ahora →</button>
        </div>

        <figure class="hero-visual">
            <img src={afterImageSrc} alt="Ambiente inmobiliario terminado con staging digital de Zynera" loading="eager" decoding="async" />
        </figure>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .btn-wizard {
        background-color: var(--accent-color);
        color: var(--bg-color);
        border: none;
        padding: 16px 32px;
        border-radius: 50px;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: var(--transition-smooth);
    }

    .btn-wizard:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(232, 194, 122, 0.2);
    }

    .hero-actions {
        margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .hero {
        padding: 160px 0 100px;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(232, 194, 122, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
    }

    .hero h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
        line-height: 1.1;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        max-width: 900px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .hero p {
        color: var(--text-dim);
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto 40px;
    }

    .hero-visual {
        margin-top: 60px;
        border-radius: 24px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        position: relative;
        aspect-ratio: 16/9;
        background: #171717;
    }

    .hero-visual img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        display: block;
        object-fit: cover;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .hero {
            padding-top: 140px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2.15rem;
            max-width: 300px;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            max-width: 280px;
        }

        .hero-visual {
            width: min(320px, calc(100vw - 80px));
            max-width: min(320px, calc(100vw - 80px));
            border-radius: 16px;
        }

        .btn-wizard {
            max-width: calc(100vw - 48px);
            padding-left: 24px;
            padding-right: 24px;
        }
    }
</style>

<script>
    document.getElementById('heroWizardBtn')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
        window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('toggle-modal'));
    });
</script>
